description: The purpose of this project is to initiate activities to support enhancement of the public administration in Turkmenistan at both policy and institutional levels.

subproject.description: The project is to ensure that all levels of governance formulate legislative and institutional frameworks and have enhanced capacities for more effective public services delivery; and that the Government integrates principles of good governance and rule of law into national policies, legislation and decision-making.
subproject.title: Civil Service Development
